{"tid":557692,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人幾個香港搭巴士驚反車或者衝落橋驚到仆街嘅路段","createTime":"2018-02-11T15:04:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T20:34:55.000Z","uid":125952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"7ec7773fae2cb12d21933334b7ad9df4ff2f77a7","tid":557692,"uid":125952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"希望大埔死者安息，傷者快啲好返！<br />\n<br />\n我先，我唔識咩路面車速，淨係知次次搭都好撚驚<br />\n<br />\n1）唔知點解荔景路啲巴士係開得勁快，搭38/40 經荔景路，轉彎入葵涌迴旋，會見到山下美孚新邨嗰個位，好驚成架車飛出攔<br />\n<br />\n2) (頭盔：離開左機場幾年唔知有無改路線）機場搭N31 經過機場警署/貨運站嗰個迴旋處，啲夜更司機唔收油，勁快鏟入去一嘢轉彎，次次去到呢度架車上層啲纖維殼都「噠噠聲」"},{"pid":"306d63d0890f7963135aff97730b354a1d206704","tid":557692,"uid":116530,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:04:56.000Z","msg":"從來唔搭巴士"},{"pid":"5049d0ebabd10f3b27e97fdef3d8cafdbd233e09","tid":557692,"uid":85819,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:06:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1ae6a1bf77e56e115608e7a9a4a51887a8bb6f28","tid":557692,"uid":13281,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:07:19.000Z","msg":"薄夫林道入般咸道果條橋<br />\n經常見d巴士側晒咁入彎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5138642aca1554bc081e2f1a1be31bc9ee0439f9","tid":557692,"uid":15745,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:08:32.000Z","msg":"東廊 上柴灣斜 每次搭118都驚跌落去"},{"pid":"feece0a7367e60f8b9cb67e695c0ad16ae007be9","tid":557692,"uid":59494,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:09:54.000Z","msg":"山道天橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61eae5a8f3a0037248266e963f149f71cf4adb2f","tid":557692,"uid":157521,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T15:12:13.000Z","msg":"970/970x 班車手出完西隧落斜轉右去高樂花園<br />\n順燈一路去黎個大U-turn<br />\n朝朝full load都好驚反車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5c8b290de607ac8003ac3cddbdc5084a4f41698","tid":